---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Tools Expertise">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-wrench"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Industry-standard Testing Tools Expertise</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies gives organisations the ability to perform automated tests using the industry-standard tools used in software testing. We help your business determine which performance evaluation method is best suited for your needs, cutting down testing durations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-cogs"></i></div>
            <h5>Functional &amp; Regression</h5>
            <p>WinRunner, SilkTest and QuickTest Pro for automated functional and regression testing across your application suite.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-bar-chart"></i></div>
            <h5>Load Testing</h5>
            <p>LoadRunner and SilkPerformer for comprehensive load and performance benchmarking under realistic traffic conditions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-flask"></i></div>
            <h5>Unit Testing</h5>
            <p>Jprobe and JUnit for comprehensive unit test coverage and memory leak detection across Java-based applications.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-bug"></i></div>
            <h5>Defect &amp; Change Tracking</h5>
            <p>Bugzilla, Test Director, Silk Central Test Manager and Issue Manager for systematic defect and change tracking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-tv"></i></div>
            <h5>GUI Testing</h5>
            <p>Mercury WinRunner, QTP and SilkTest for thorough graphical user interface testing across all screen types and resolutions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-folder-open-o"></i></div>
            <h5>Configuration Management</h5>
            <p>CVS, VSS and StarTeam for version control, configuration management and project tracking across the delivery lifecycle.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
